# Customer OnBoarding System

A full‑stack customer onboarding web application built with **React (Vite)** for the frontend and **Node.js + Express** for the backend.  
This project demonstrates a basic customer onboarding workflow including UI pages and backend APIs.

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- React.js (via Vite)
- Tailwind CSS (utility‑first styling)
- JavaScript

**Backend**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- REST‑style API routing

**Other**
- Axios (for HTTP requests from frontend)
- nodemon (for backend development)

---

## 📁 Project Structure


Customer‑OnBoarding‑System/
│
├─ backend/ # Express backend APIs
│ ├─ config/ # Configuration files
│ ├─ controllers/ # API logic
│ ├─ models/ # Data models (if using DB)
│ ├─ routes/ # API route definitions
│ ├─ services/ # Backend utilities/services
│ ├─ app.js # Express app setup
│ └─ server.js # Server entry point
│
├─ frontend/ # React + Vite frontend
│ ├─ public/ # Static assets
│ ├─ src/ # React source files
│ ├─ package.json
│ └─ README.md # Vite React template readme
│
├─ .gitignore
└─ package‑lock.json

